snippet.title: Best VGM 752 - Klonoa - Untamed Heart (Vision 6-1)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1078 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c_ex2h9t2yk
Best VGM 2029 - https://youtu.be/CHd4iWEFARM

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation / Nintendo Wii
Klonoa (1998)
Untamed Heart (Vision 6-1)
Eriko Imura
